column2: SELECT m.id, n.objid, n.distance, o.petroMag_u-o.extinction_u as u_pmag,    o.petroMag_g-o.extinction_g as g_pmag, o.petroMag_r-o.extinction_r as r_pmag,    o.petroMag_i-o.extinction_i as i_pmag, o.petroMag_z-o.extinction_z as z_pmag,    E_bv=extinction_r/#, kcorrR0# as k0# FROM MyDB.temp AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n    LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid=o.objid JOIN Photoz as h    on h.objid=o.objid order by id
